column5: Hey folks, Looks like we have some storms moving through again. Chatham, London and the north shore of Erie have storm watches in affect and the Ottawa area has storm warnings. If your heading out tonight, keep an eye on the sky! HH
HH They are saying it will make a full circle. Southern to the east up to the north then back down.Lots of power packed in this one.  Carefull out there folks if yer out and about on the waters.
im down in leamington for business again and there is tornado warnings down here right now.  Still sunny though but apparently its on the way.  Cheers!
The crops of southern ontario need rain badly. rumour  has it farmers are calling in crop insurance south of woodstock. and simcoe area.
Nothing here yesterday,  & yes we need this rain bad in our erea.
Cancelled here in the Barrie area.Did get the isulated down pour.
yep and I got soaked in it today while fishing for carp. Landed 3 before the rain got me all soaked. Nothing big so I won't bother posting it.  dsn
